# UI patterns

## Home screen

- **Quick Play** — green `btn-play` (primary action)
- **Oóc Om Bóc Festival** — yellow `btn-festival`
- Secondary menu: Story, Daily, Leaderboard, **Settings only** (no separate offline shortcut)
- Home is scrollable — avoid cutting off bottom buttons

## Settings screen (order)

1. PWA / offline install (top, blue-tinted section)
2. Network status
3. Offline feature list
4. Preferences (sound)
5. Data (clear progress, pending sync)

## PWA UX (simplified)

- Show **Install app** button when `beforeinstallprompt` fires
- Otherwise show **one platform hint** (iOS / Android / desktop)
- Full 3-step guide lives in collapsed `<details>` — not shown by default
- Dev-only note when install prompt unavailable on localhost

## Styles

- Global styles: `src/styles/main.css`
- Match existing button classes: `btn`, `btn-primary`, `btn-secondary`, `btn-play`, `btn-festival`
